{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aeaa1264c0","title":"论自由结合公开分配的好处","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"81c0551b6a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"aeaa1264c0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"25804569a0","name":"蒋兴仁"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0c8c3bbeec","type":"title","text":"论自由结合公开分配的好处","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"abb9f67341","type":"authors","text":"北京大学蒋兴仁","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"e124efbd7e","type":"subtitle","text":"（蒋兴仁：北京大学生物系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"a6f9c0e7de","type":"subtitle","text":"大字报二则：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"69942be0fd","type":"subtitle","text":"一、论自由结合公开分配的好处","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"da5192a431","type":"paragraph","text":"同意地四同学意见，赞成分配毕业生时公布要“人”单位需要人数，工作性质、内容、地点，和要“人”条件让同学直接与工作单位联系，了解情况，然后广泛讨论充份协商，由用“人”单位根据同学自愿决定分配结果。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"c4a7e00b34","type":"paragraph","text":"其好处如下：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"03da8efd26","type":"appellation","text":"①发挥同学主人翁思想。易和集体利益结合。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"500499399b","type":"paragraph","text":"②彻底消灭官僚主义。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"16e811c001","type":"paragraph","text":"③ 同学直接联系可以了解情况……更对口径。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"1a1efaa1d1","type":"paragraph","text":"④同学充份协商可以加强团结。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"85f76982e5","type":"paragraph","text":"⑤ 可使工作单位选择机会，工作困难有志士自愿前往。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"5acd05368e","type":"paragraph","text":"⑥ 可以限制个别觉悟低同学对祖国无限要求，于有限实际范围之内暴露其无理要求于大庭广众之中。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"d423546027","type":"paragraph","text":"⑦可以使同学了解国家情况，提高政治觉悟。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"3d822b1b68","type":"paragraph","text":" 生四　蒋兴仁","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"3090a2860d","type":"subtitle","text":"二、论考勤制度的缺点","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"46648380b4","type":"paragraph","text":"考勤制度是从工厂硬扯过来的，硬套于智力劳动的形式主义的产物。它不但没有鼓舞同学学习积极性，反而限制了同学们的学习的发展。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"d43f6e03e7","type":"paragraph","text":"请看一下，它的缺点：","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"a2053e7a10","type":"paragraph","text":"1．只讲究形式上的出勤，不能保证学好与听好。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"d8f9d9f3d9","type":"paragraph","text":"2．由行政指命而作点名汇报的班长，陷于忙乱。并且把同学当作职员，是对同学不尊重。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"},{"id":"8aa8ee96e0","type":"paragraph","text":"3．强迫同学出勤听课，是对教学质量不高的教师的偏袒与怂恿不能刺激教员提高教学质量，而反使他洋洋自喜，“好不好，反正总有人来听”。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0"}],"page":{"id":"2cacb4dc2c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"aeaa1264c0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}